Title: 1959 INGRAHAM EAGLE DOLLAR POCKET WATCH Wind Up KEEPS GOOD TIME
Description: I have not found many of these Ingraham EAGLE pocket Watches, I am assuming it is fairly rare, but I do not know for certain. Purchased with 5 or 6 other Pocket Watches from a collector who was "thinning" his collection, this is running & seems to keep excellent time. The only marking on the Dial is "EAGLE", then at the very bottom it is marked USA. I Opened the back of the watch & found that it was marked with the following: THE INGRAHAM WATCH COMPANY Bristol Conn. Under the mfg'er is the number "59" which I assume means that this windup watch was made in 1959. Please view the pictures carefully as they are a very large part of my description.
